data.name: About_ContactInformation
data.value: If you have any question, idea or suggestion about this app, or if you want to report some specific problem, please contact us using [url="https://trello.com/b/MwqpL8Bw/content-manager"]Trello[/url] or [url="https://trello.com/c/w5xT6ssZ/49-contacts"]something else[/url].
